Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.53,0:02:07.44,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起　Chance Chance 許願
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.51,0:02:08.41,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jump Jump 掀起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:10.70,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fun Fun 夢想　Shout Shout 傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:14.04,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失誤的話就當排練再來一回！
