Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.33,0:22:31.12,EDC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,heat heat　激情難以遏制
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.60,0:22:35.15,EDC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's shock shock　衝擊發信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.32,0:22:38.29,EDC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論何處都攜手向前
