Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.98,0:00:26.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  唯  起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.07,0:00:29.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  唯  快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.83,0:00:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  憂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是週日
