Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  要吃蛋糕啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.21,0:00:57.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  你們騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.18,0:00:58.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.32,0:01:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不行  紬  把真蛋糕拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.39,0:01:03.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.74,0:01:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田井中同學
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.67,0:01:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.10,0:01:09.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.30,0:01:14.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前借給你們的布偶裝差不多該還了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.44,0:01:16.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演劇社好像要用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.66,0:01:17.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布偶裝？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.28,0:01:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律  你還沒還嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.10,0:01:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.77,0:01:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前段時間為了招攬新人穿過後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.49,0:01:28.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就放到儲藏室裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.32,0:01:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是還回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.55,0:01:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.82,0:01:34.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想  布偶裝的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.43,0:01:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.14,0:01:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.31,0:01:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕音豬…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.33,0:03:29.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我們來大掃除
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.07,0:03:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個  別露出這麼一副明顯不想幹的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.95,0:03:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  今天加油來練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得沒錯  小律
