Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼不想幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
