Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是滿是私人物品  而是只有私人物品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:08.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說得沒錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～我的呱呱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就來收拾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:14.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明之前放得好好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.49,0:04:15.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了不要放回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.03,0:04:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法  就認真地來幹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:21.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這量還真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼私人物品的話  都暫且把這裡當作倉庫堆著了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.69,0:04:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這成堆的布偶是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個大的只用了二百日元就入手了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.51,0:04:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又沒問你那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:41.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  這個也一起拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  這個不是我的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:44.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？那…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是澪的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.13,0:04:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然把咖啡套具也帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.59,0:04:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但結果都沒用過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  餐具櫥也要掃除嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.60,0:04:59.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  難得掃除一次  就順便一起收拾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.31,0:05:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新來看一下的話  好像真的很昂貴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.27,0:05:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些餐具要多少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…價格我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:12.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但聽說和比利時王室用的是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.23,0:05:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王室？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.65,0:05:16.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.55,0:05:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大部分都收拾好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.91,0:05:22.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.02,0:05:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我們的私人物品也有很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:29.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是以前輕音社的私人物品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.29,0:05:32.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前好像有很多社員呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也曾經認真幹過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:37.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了個東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.41,0:05:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈  好像很貴重的箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有裝什麼值錢的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:49.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:54.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很舊  但好像很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還期待會出現更有趣的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:05:58.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.57,0:06:01.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是輕音社  應該感興趣才對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  好懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.72,0:06:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.37,0:06:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  這是老師的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.67,0:06:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然都沒怎麼用過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:15.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師以前是輕音社嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  我沒說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:20.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  果然是那樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:24.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園祭的時候演奏得非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:29.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有段空白期  但比現在的小唯要彈得好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:31.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次教教我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.77,0:06:32.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便說一下  這個就是學生時期的小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:38.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.80,0:06:39.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私人物品大家都會各自拿回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以小佐和也拿回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:46.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:50.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好濃的霉味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:53.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也沒時間來彈了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那這個吉他怎麼處理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:07:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它賣到店裡去  來增加社費吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.74,0:07:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真大方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.32,0:07:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個塞給我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.97,0:07:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  這個不是好東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是從我爸爸的朋友那裡得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種保存狀態的話  已經不行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  如果能賣掉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.95,0:07:23.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓別人去用  對它來說也是一種幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.35,0:07:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚～好濃的霉味～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:30.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好過分～盡讓我來拿～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.60,0:07:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜拳三連敗是你自己不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:35.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.11,0:07:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的包也很重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.57,0:07:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是你自己的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:45.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就到時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.42,0:07:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.06,0:07:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定不會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:52.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我把你打回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.61,0:08:00.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像小孩子一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:01.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:03.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.35,0:08:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  看見了  這是剪刀？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.33,0:08:08.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬紬  不能說出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  澪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:12.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來猜拳啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.79,0:08:13.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才拿的傳單？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些東西能放在準備室裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫥櫃？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.34,0:08:22.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一個就能把很多東西整理進去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:24.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.36,0:08:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個價格的話  用社費也能買
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看  傢俱賣場在…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是Home Center？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬紬？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.93,0:08:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多方便的商品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.44,0:08:44.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小不同的電燈泡之類的  七色的塑膠膠帶之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.78,0:08:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…有是有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬  你是第一次來Home Center嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:49.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都想要來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.46,0:08:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:09:00.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  唯  吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.11,0:09:04.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀哎呀哎呀  好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  這是能很漂亮地修補牆破洞的筆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.12,0:09:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.25,0:09:14.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是能輕鬆整理舊雜誌的膠帶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.73,0:09:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼稀奇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個擦水龍頭就會變得閃亮閃亮？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:23.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬學姐  還有這種東西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:31.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能把蛋糕精確地八等分的切蛋糕刀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.28,0:09:33.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像傘一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用這個切嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來下  來下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  快看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.02,0:09:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多螺絲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯學姐也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些全都是螺絲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.03,0:09:46.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:47.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  快看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:48.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好酷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電動螺絲槍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.14,0:09:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砰  砰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.47,0:09:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  真吵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  你們兩個死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不不…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:03.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.51,0:10:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯真是小孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:08.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好刺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:11.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快摘掉  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.54,0:10:14.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.28,0:10:16.59,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要隨便亂弄店裡的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.69,0:10:18.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  好痛好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:18.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵  梓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次又是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.61,0:10:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿這個動起來很方便哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:23.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太鬆了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為演唱會時穿的衣服怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在背後寫上「放學後茶會」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴走族嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐和子老師說可以放在活動室裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.84,0:10:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那讓他們明天放學後送到學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.63,0:10:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯她們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這附近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.55,0:10:46.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  紬來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你買了多少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.21,0:11:00.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏龜？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:01.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.69,0:11:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:04.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.94,0:11:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方請不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.63,0:11:10.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:13.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好可愛的鱉啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是鱉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在鱉之中也是脫穎而出的美人啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…這是豬鼻龜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:25.29,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（豬鼻龜（Pig-Nosed Turtle），又稱飛河龜（Fly River Turtle），\N學名Carettochelys insculpta）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是烏龜  烏龜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.39,0:11:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛得想把花生放進它鼻子裡～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.61,0:11:32.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算是什麼可愛的程度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.66,0:11:39.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到從那裡開始會是四連敗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:40.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝利的剪刀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:42.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就讓我來核定一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:43.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:49.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:55.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的樂隊要是有這麼多人的話  會演奏出怎樣的音樂來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  要是有這麼多社員就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.01,0:12:04.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待核定的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.07,0:12:12.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個吉他  我們用五十萬日元買下了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.28,0:12:16.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十萬日元？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.31,0:12:20.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:26.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩您了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.94,0:12:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:29.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.57,0:12:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是…五五五…五百萬…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮定點  價位都變了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.86,0:12:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.22,0:12:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也太淡定了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.14,0:12:42.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會是這個價啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是在照顧紬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.75,0:12:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  和那個沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這把吉他的原型為1960年代最初的吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.26,0:12:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當初材料和造型都沒有固定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過各種局部改造之後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才成為現在的模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:04.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位帶來的這把吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指板是一種叫做藍花楹的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:06.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（指板(fingerboard)：特指除拇指以外四個手指接觸部分的木材）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現今非常貴重的木材製成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.25,0:13:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是出高價的原因之一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺憾的是  這把吉他的系弦板被更換過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:21.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是完全原裝  所以價格稍微下降了些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.31,0:13:25.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但停條系弦板更有演奏性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.31,0:13:25.01,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（停條系弦板(Stop Tailpiece)：六孔穿弦金屬條式，屬於最常見的類型，延音效果不錯）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:27.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多顧客更偏愛這種
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也算不上太大的缺點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這把吉他被長期封存
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:36.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有過多損傷琴身和琴格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:36.09,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（琴格(fret)：鑲嵌於指板的薄金屬細條，用於改變弦的音高）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為年代物來說條件非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.39,0:13:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就以這個價格收購了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.49,0:13:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總…總之是很貴重的吉他！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:48.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厚！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.67,0:13:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是巨無霸嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:53.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒講漢堡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.15,0:13:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說薯條是不是太多了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這麼多錢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薯條XL Size
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.51,0:14:02.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用找了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你花了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:06.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  這個是自掏腰包
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這樣好嗎  大家分？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:14.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法吧  小佐和都說用作社費了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼唧哼唧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.87,0:14:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.78,0:14:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧！五個人平分一人十萬！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.78,0:14:26.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個效果器挺想要來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵陷落
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.79,0:14:31.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！別把那麼多錢拿出來炫耀！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:34.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看～澪也有十萬哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十萬啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.19,0:14:39.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有十萬…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要多重貝司音箱模擬和新的放大器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.42,0:14:48.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要雙踏板和落地鼓啦 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.73,0:14:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等錢上臉的感覺如何啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～繼續～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:58.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…各位？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:15:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡這裡～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.22,0:15:04.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.06,0:15:06.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收拾得很乾淨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:09.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說好了私人物品拿回家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.71,0:15:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  除了昨天帶回去的還剩下這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.95,0:15:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是再往回搬  一定會惹憂生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:26.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是放在這裡  生氣的人就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.98,0:15:29.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憂才嚇人呢  昨天她還那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.69,0:15:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒了我吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全都沒有姐姐的威嚴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.38,0:15:39.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  過後我一定收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.03,0:15:41.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先在這裡放一陣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊  只能放這些哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:46.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:49.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀呵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫥櫃送來啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:55.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  感覺不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.49,0:15:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？人家和你們說話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.51,0:16:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.47,0:16:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和～怎麼你來啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.71,0:16:12.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家都沒聽到～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.48,0:16:14.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是  昨天怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.65,0:16:15.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  昨天？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:18.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的吉他啊  賣了多少錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那個啊…賣了多少來著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.91,0:16:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得…好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因…因為挺老的  好像50年前的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:30.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.27,0:16:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？那麼說小佐和其實已經是50歲的人啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.37,0:16:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪裡見過這麼精神的50歲！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:41.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說過是我爸爸的朋友送的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:46.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來的確…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:49.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是  到底賣了多少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:51.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這  這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.31,0:16:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…一萬元
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:56.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也太貪了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:01.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉…順口就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然也就那麼點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.21,0:17:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都發霉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:08.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把發票給我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.30,0:17:10.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要算進社費裡的  當然需要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.15,0:17:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你難道沒要？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:19.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.48,0:17:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.81,0:17:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉啦～勇者啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.60,0:17:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快吃！快吃！快吃！快吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼！快吐出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.17,0:17:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒門！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.50,0:17:40.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給老娘吐出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.84,0:17:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.89,0:17:43.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘔…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧！賣了五十萬？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也太厲害了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.37,0:17:52.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是非常貴重的東西！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還請恕罪！小的本無意隱瞞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:17:59.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但金額龐大  小的一時動了邪念…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.19,0:18:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太骯髒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.88,0:18:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她從前就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.50,0:18:05.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們有什麼資格說我！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  那就把小律說的一萬元當作社費好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便頂上櫥櫃錢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.45,0:18:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～就那麼點？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.37,0:18:18.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是一開始就講實話的話  我還打算全給你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.38,0:18:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你絕對在騙人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.63,0:18:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是律不好  不知道你想藏什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.72,0:18:30.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  我本來就覺得直接說出來比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.26,0:18:31.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然還有臉說！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.36,0:18:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後我還有一個願望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用那疊錢來抽…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽我的臉吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太幸福了～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:46.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是你好啊…真和諧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.36,0:18:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.13,0:18:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再特別讓你們用這筆錢買一件東西好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.12,0:18:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想買什麼  大家商量好再說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.87,0:18:59.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一件啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.79,0:19:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說一個啦  我要來五個！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.77,0:19:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要臉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.43,0:19:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.01,0:19:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,添個放大器最合適了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.26,0:19:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是覺得效果器比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪樣都不是大家都能用的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.08,0:19:19.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提議！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:20.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多買一隻呱呱如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.98,0:19:25.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一對的話  絕對會有新社員加入的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.98,0:19:26.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.79,0:19:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎呱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:31.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,球拍不要握得太緊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.76,0:19:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用全身的力量去打球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光用手勁的話  手腕和手肘會痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.48,0:19:39.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.89,0:19:43.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪個社團都有新社員加入並正式開始活動了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.34,0:19:44.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:46.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.83,0:19:51.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.24,0:19:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…雖然說「五個人就好了」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.24,0:19:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但終究是想要個學妹的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:20:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也這麼覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.85,0:20:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.38,0:20:07.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵來的時候  我們都很高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.08,0:20:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法  那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪位新同學…請帶我去音樂室…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:17.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個已經試過了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:19.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.76,0:20:25.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想到個好主意！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.81,0:20:35.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.60,0:20:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是新成員小豬～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.99,0:20:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託老師買回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓的學妹哦  多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:53.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  不覺得反應太淡了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.88,0:20:55.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.63,0:20:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說梓喜歡這烏龜的可是唯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.05,0:21:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時梓喵明明一副很想要的樣子盯著看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.60,0:21:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯著看的是唯學姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:09.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是覺得那張臉好怪而看看而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.98,0:21:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.56,0:21:12.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞砸了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.27,0:21:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.85,0:21:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但為什麼突然這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.59,0:21:20.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.66,0:21:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們覺得小梓沒有學妹是不是寂寞了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.55,0:21:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.24,0:21:28.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄來了新人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.26,0:21:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  被這麼隨便的人買來養  太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.89,0:21:45.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點頭了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:47.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.19,0:21:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  今後我來好好照顧你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.61,0:21:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  我也會好好照顧的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.90,0:21:57.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯學姐做不來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:22:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.13,0:23:45.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.86,0:23:46.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.09,0:23:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從成為班主任後
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.91,0:23:51.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和變得皮膚滑滑～頭髮亮亮～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.06,0:23:54.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不覺得她異常充實嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.04,0:23:56.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想閃閃發光！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.86,0:24:00.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  它在看小唯了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.42,0:24:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮儀很不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.16,0:24:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正像這樣在黑暗中思考著閃閃發光小律大作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.95,0:24:09.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？


